      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/Knowledge\" title=\"Knowledge\">Knowledge</a> * <a href=\"/Endgame_Tablebases\" title=\"Endgame Tablebases\">Endgame Tablebases</a> * FinalGen</b>\n</p><p><b>FinalGen</b>,<br />\na chess endgame tablebase generator for <a href=\"/Windows\" title=\"Windows\">Windows</a> written by <a href=\"/Pedro_P%C3%A9rez_Romero\" title=\"Pedro Pérez Romero\">Pedro Pérez Romero</a>, able to solve chess positions with up to one piece per side, and almost any number of pawns, despite some complexity limitations regarding <a href=\"/Memory\" title=\"Memory\">memory</a>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Screenshot\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Screenshot</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#See_also\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">See also</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Publications\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Publications</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#2012\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2012</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#2020_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2020 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Screenshot\">Screenshot</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=FinalGen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Screenshot\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"http://finalgenchess.ovh/home_ing.php\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"Finalgengui.jpg\" src=\"/images/b/b2/Finalgengui.jpg\" width=\"516\" height=\"348\" style=\"vertical-align: text-bottom\" class=\"thumbborder\" /></a></div> \n<p>FinalGen <a href=\"/GUI\" title=\"GUI\">GUI</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> \n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=FinalGen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: See also\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Freezer\" title=\"Freezer\">Freezer</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/GAFS\" title=\"GAFS\">GAFS</a> </li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Publications\">Publications</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=FinalGen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Publications\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Guy_Haworth\" title=\"Guy Haworth\">Guy Haworth</a> (<b>2015</b>). <i>Chess Endgame News</i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#38_1\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal, Vol. 38, No. 1</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/Crafty\" title=\"Crafty\">Crafty</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Karsten_M%C3%BCller\" title=\"Karsten Müller\">Karsten Müller</a>, <a href=\"/Guy_Haworth\" title=\"Guy Haworth\">Guy Haworth</a> (<b>2019</b>). <i>FinalGen revisited: new discoveries</i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#41_1\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal, Vol. 41, No. 1</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=FinalGen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2012\">2012</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=FinalGen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: 2012\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://kirill-kryukov.com/chess/discussion-board/viewtopic.php?f=6&amp;t=6523\">7 8 or more pieces tablebase generator</a> by <a href=\"/Pedro_P%C3%A9rez_Romero\" title=\"Pedro Pérez Romero\">Pedro Pérez Romero</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">CCRL Discussion Board</a>, March 16, 2012</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=42921\">NEWS: FinalGen chess endgame tablebase generator</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Jes%C3%BAs_Mu%C3%B1oz&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Jesús Muñoz (page does not exist)\">Jesús Muñoz</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 18, 2012</li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=42921&amp;start=32\">Re: NEWS: FinalGen chess endgame tablebase generator</a> by <a href=\"/Pedro_P%C3%A9rez_Romero\" title=\"Pedro Pérez Romero\">Pedro Pérez Romero</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 27, 2012</dd>\n<dd> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=42921&amp;start=33\">Re: NEWS: FinalGen chess endgame tablebase generator</a> by <a href=\"/Pedro_P%C3%A9rez_Romero\" title=\"Pedro Pérez Romero\">Pedro Pérez Romero</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 27, 2012</dd></dl>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://rybkaforum.net/cgi-bin/rybkaforum/topic_show.pl?tid=24565\">FinalGen</a> by Dhanish, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Rybka Forum</a>, March 19, 2012</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2020_...\">2020 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=FinalGen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: 2020 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=73481&amp;start=7\">Re: Using Freeware AI and Dynamically Generated Endgame Tablebases</a> by <a href=\"/Bojun_Guo\" title=\"Bojun Guo\">noobpwnftw</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 28, 2020 </li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=FinalGen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://finalgenchess.ovh/home_ing.php\">FinalGen chess endgame tablebase generator</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://finalgenchess.ovh/phpBB3/viewforum.php?f=3\">FinalGen EndGame Generator Forum</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=FinalGen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://finalgenchess.ovh/home_ing.php\">FinalGen chess endgame tablebase generator</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/Endgame_Tablebases\" title=\"Endgame Tablebases\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260228171425\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.012 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.013 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 49/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 86/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key oscar70_mw1-mw_:pcache:idhash:4451-0!canonical and timestamp 20260228171425 and revision id 21797\n -->\n"
